    • Method Detail

      • getreloadable

        Boolean getreloadable()
        Returns:
        'true' if the session is reload-able. For a session to be reload-able it should be 1) disconnected, 2) locked (or blocked) and 3) its session manager de-active

      • getconnections

        ObjectName[] getconnections()
        Returns:
        Object names of all connection elements under this session. Can be empty

      • getsessionManager

        ObjectName getsessionManager()
        Returns:
        Object name of the session manager element under this session. Cannot be null

      • getpersister

      • getencryption
